comment: Foul is warranted; however there is a foul commited by Foye (DEN) prior to it for grabbing the arm of Evans (NOP).
Gordon (NOP) makes contact with the arm of Lawson (DEN) and the contact affects his movement to the basket.
Chandler (DEN) grabs the arm of Asik (NOP) after he secures the rebound.
OOB correctly awarded to New Orleans.
Barton (DEN) commits a take foul on Gordon (NOP).
Cole (NOP) makes contact with the body of Gallinari (DEN) and the contact affects his movement to the basket.
Cunningham (NOP) clamps Chandler's (DEN) arm, preventing him from getting to the rebound.
After communication with the Replay Center, the call is upheld.
Ball is awarded to New Orleans and referees initiate replay to confirm.
Chandler (DEN) commits a take foul on Fredette (NOP).
Lawson (DEN) commits a take foul on Cole (NOP).
Lawson (DEN) commits a take foul on Evans (NOP).
Chandler (DEN) commits the take foul on Evans (NOP).
